{"tid":1471970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自己鍾意嘅歌手/明人/藝人 從來冇支持過自己嘅感覺真係好難受","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:13:30.000Z","uid":199716,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8f325377f585e39aa7a63d46274d8a0caf6b78","tid":1471970,"uid":199716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"唔係製造白色恐佈 唔係逼人表態 只係講出第一身感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n細細個開始鍾意到依家嘅偶像 睇到佢地個個發聲明話自己擁護中華人民共和國 堅決反對示威亂港 等等 <br />\n<br />\n又話者從來冇為自己爭取緊啲正確嘅嘢 例如要普選 民主 甚至香港人加油 哩啲咁大路 明明毫無錯嘅地方 佢地哪怕係一句都唔肯講 <br />\n<br />\n每次諗起會反思最後一班愛香港 捍衛香港嘅人好孤立無援 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔係抱住「唔係我地捧你 你紅得起？你可以撈得咁掂？」嘅心態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係的確  我地特登比錢睇你拍嘅係 比錢買你嘅歌 比錢入你演唱會就係為左目睹自己偶像一次 為嘅係咩？只係因為自己真係好喜歡 好認同 好崇拜果個人 但係換來嘅  係原來佢同自己從來冇試過同一陣線<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地肯幫我地出一句聲 其實已經好振奮人心 好鼓舞 可惜哩種感覺從來冇降臨 <br />\n<br />\n真係好難受 同時間又要同自己講一定要捱落去 唉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5075c36be47bf33745309dd1c28e350fc408e84","tid":1471970,"uid":171992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s=